{"tid":2509464,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"索尼年度淨利潤首破1萬億日元大關","createTime":"2021-04-29T12:28:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T14:31:04.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd7a001f92fb976458908640d1ae98f0251b0fe3","tid":2509464,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0428%2F4ddec179p00qsa0810054c000hr00bug.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0428%252F4ddec179p00qsa0810054c000hr00bug.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=b202b599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據日本經濟新聞報導，索尼28日公佈截至2021年3月財年合併財務業績（US GAAP）。財報顯示，淨利潤較上一財年增長一倍，達到1.1717萬億日元（合107.50億美元），首次突破1萬億日元大關，並創下兩年來新高。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  同時，銷售額同比增長9％，達到8.9993萬億日元。新冠疫情持續擴散，宅經濟帶動包括遊戲、音樂、電影在內的娛樂業務銷售額增加13%，至4.3549萬億日元，佔總銷售額的5成。其中，由於半導體短缺引起關注的&ldquo; PS5&rdquo;的銷量也超過780萬部的目標。"},{"pid":"ff19188bb861e5790739724f6789f54fbbeeb7e9","tid":2509464,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"索尼越黎越掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e776b706bafe67e1e64a855c64d5f8d68234f5b1","tid":2509464,"uid":8011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff19188bb861e5790739724f6789f54fbbeeb7e9","tid":2509464,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"索尼越黎越掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"手機業務唔洗睇，依然係虧損。"},{"pid":"80478ef24865a2f18205e5db2333477b90c665c0","tid":2509464,"uid":134774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"罪大"},{"pid":"b16e092a9d6c399896c3b198d9eb321cf8c6db32","ti